<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="296" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1892,1990]" pageId="2" pageNumber="296">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1928,1954]" pageId="2" pageNumber="296">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name is an amalgam of the names of William Kirby and Heinrich Prell in recognition of their contributions to the nomenclature of the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="MacLeay" authorityYear="1819" box="[607,737,1964,1990]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Dynastinae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="2" pageNumber="299" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Dynastinae</taxonomicName>
. The name is masculine in gender.
</paragraph>
